detailedDescription.articleBody:
Ariel Aquino Muhlach, commonly known as Aga Muhlach, is a multi-award winning Filipino actor and product endorser.
He was introduced to the entertainment industry using his real name "Ariel Muhlach" at the age of seven when he appeared in the 1975 film May Isang Tsuper ng Taksi and the 1976 film, Babaing Hiwalay Sa Asawa, but he only became well known with the success of the 1984 film Bagets, after which he became a popular matinee idol.
